name: Western Indo Fusion Saree
description:

https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi - commissions open!
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

Western Indo Fusion Saree

We are back today in the world of Fusion Design for the purpose of reinventing and modernizing the Indian Saree with is a staple of South-Indian fashion, and a well renown piece of fashion throughout the globe!

In fact Saree is so popular that it is quite hard to make a LoRA that beats native SD at generating traditional saree.

Therefore, I have decided to take the route of fusion design to find a blind spot and make something that the AI is incapable of making without this LoRA.

Based on my experiments, I can assure you that it is unlikely that the AI can pull off this type of Western Indo Fusion Design!

Please tell me what you think of this new model in the review and comments section!

Get this LoRA and start designing
